name: mfa
description:
recorded live on 2018 at universidad nacional de las artes, buenos aires, argentina

collecting this piece on primary includes a 1/1 diy cassette tape, with this track and an unreleased side b. alongside the tape the collector will get a set of stickers from my generative art nfts, shipped to anywhere in the planet (earth). it also includes codes for downloading all my current and future releases on bandcamp in the best possible quality.

collecting this piece on secondary collector will get codes for downloading all my current and future releases on bandcamp in the best possible quality.


this is the first of a series of 1/1 music nft / cassette tapes of my albums, singles and eps
